io.permazen.kv.mvstore

Class ByteArrayDataType

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.permazen.kv.mvstore.ByteArrayDataType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.h2.mvstore.type.DataType

    public final class ByteArrayDataType
extends Object
implements org.h2.mvstore.type.DataType
    MVStore DataType for byte[] arrays sorted lexicographically.

    When keys are encoded in bulk, prefix compression is applied via KeyListEncoder.
